| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3650 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 484d72bc-6332-5678-9f20-d7a4b6949020"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
